SOURCE: https://github.com/caido/doc-developer/blob/main/src/reference/modules/llrt/stream.md#2025-04-20_snippet_37

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function write(data, cb) {
  if (!stream.write(data)) {
    stream.once('drain', cb);
  } else {
    process.nextTick(cb);
  }
}

// Wait for cb to be called before doing any other write.
write('hello', () => {
  console.log('Write completed, do more writes now.');
});
```

